        fw_s01_num: 'Section 01', fw_s01_h2: 'Instrument and Scope Definition',
        fw_s01_p1: 'This framework governs the execution of a structured, rules-based trading discipline challenge. The challenge is confined to the following operational parameters:',
        fw_s01_li1: '<strong>Instrument:</strong> US100 (NASDAQ-100 Index CFD or equivalent) — <em>exclusively</em>. No other instruments are permitted under any circumstance.',
        fw_s01_li2: '<strong>Duration:</strong> 2 calendar months from the date of activation.',
        fw_s01_li3: '<strong>Session:</strong> New York session only (09:30–16:00 ET). No pre-market, London, or Asian session trading is authorized.',
        fw_s01_mandate: '<strong>Binding Constraint:</strong> Any execution on a non-designated instrument, or outside the specified session window, constitutes an immediate and irrevocable invalidation of the challenge.',
        fw_s02_num: 'Section 02', fw_s02_h2: 'Nature of the Framework',
        fw_s02_p1: 'This framework constitutes a <strong>behavioral and process validation system</strong>. It is designed to separate disciplined operators from reactive participants by imposing strict structural boundaries on execution behavior.',
        fw_s02_p2: 'This framework is <strong>not</strong> any of the following:',
        fw_s02_li1: 'An investment advisory service', fw_s02_li2: 'A signal service or trade alert system',
        fw_s02_li3: 'Financial advice of any kind', fw_s02_li4: 'A profit guarantee or implied return promise',
        fw_s02_li5: 'A copy trading system or managed execution service',
        fw_s02_p3: 'Participants who enter this challenge expecting guaranteed returns have fundamentally misunderstood its purpose. This is a process validation framework — not a performance guarantee.',
        fw_s03_num: 'Section 03', fw_s03_h2: 'Participant Eligibility',
        fw_s03_p1: 'This framework is designed for participants who meet the following criteria:',
        fw_s03_li1: 'Currently trade live or simulated accounts with regularity',
        fw_s03_li2: 'Possess understanding of market structure, price action, and risk management fundamentals',
        fw_s03_li3: 'Accept that process violations carry greater consequence than financial loss',
        fw_s03_li4: 'Are prepared to submit to strict external rule enforcement over a 2-month period',
        fw_s03_mandate: '<strong>Eligibility Restriction:</strong> This framework is not suitable for complete beginners. It is not designed for participants seeking guaranteed returns, passive income, or market predictions.',
        fw_s04_num: 'Section 04', fw_s04_h2: 'Governing Principles',
        fw_s04_p1: 'The following principles are non-negotiable and constitute the operational foundation of this framework:',
        fw_s04_li1: '<strong>Discipline over outcome.</strong> The quality of the decision process is evaluated, not the result of any individual trade.',
        fw_s04_li2: '<strong>Process over profit.</strong> A participant who follows every rule and incurs a loss has performed at a higher standard than a participant who violates rules and generates a profit.',
        fw_s04_li3: '<strong>Rule violations constitute failure</strong> — irrespective of financial performance. No exceptions are granted.',
        fw_s04_li4: '<strong>Financial outcome carries zero evaluative weight.</strong> A profitable period achieved through rule violations is classified as a failed challenge.',
        fw_s05_num: 'Section 05', fw_s05_h2: 'Risk Governance Framework',
        fw_s05_p1: 'All risk parameters are defined before the commencement of the challenge cycle and are non-adjustable during the active period:',
        fw_s05_li1: 'Fixed fractional risk per trade — defined at cycle commencement, non-modifiable',
        fw_s05_li2: 'Strict maximum number of trades per session — defined in the participant\'s declared process',
        fw_s05_li3: 'No obligation to trade every session — a no-trade day is a correct outcome if rules are respected',
        fw_s05_li4: 'No position sizing escalation after wins or losses',
        fw_s05_li5: 'No deviation from defined risk allocation under any circumstance',
        fw_s06_num: 'Section 06', fw_s06_h2: 'Mandatory Execution Rules',
        fw_s06_p1: 'All participants must commit to the following provisions without exception:',
        fw_s06_li1: 'Predefined trading windows only — no execution outside declared session hours',
        fw_s06_li2: 'Rule-based entries and exits — no discretionary overrides',
        fw_s06_li3: 'Structural stop-loss placement — no emotional or arbitrary adjustment',
        fw_s06_li4: 'Scenario-based profit taking — exits defined before entry, not after',
        fw_s06_li5: 'Immediate invalidation of broken setups — if the setup is gone, the trade is gone',
        fw_s06_li6: 'Zero re-entries after missed trades — missed is missed',
        fw_s06_li7: 'No revenge trading — losses do not justify additional entries',
        fw_s06_li8: 'No impulsive entries — every trade requires documented pre-conditions',
        fw_s06_li9: 'No deviation from defined risk — position sizing and stop placement are non-negotiable',
        fw_s06_mandate: '<strong>Enforcement:</strong> Violation of any single provision immediately invalidates the challenge. There are no warnings, no second chances, and no exceptions. The rules exist as the structural boundary of the challenge. Removal of any boundary renders the exercise void.',
        fw_s07_num: 'Section 07', fw_s07_h2: 'Evaluation Criteria',
        fw_s07_p1: 'Participants are evaluated strictly on the following behavioral and procedural metrics:',
        fw_s07_li1: 'Adherence to session restrictions',
        fw_s07_li2: 'Compliance with risk limits (position sizing, stop-loss, daily exposure)',
        fw_s07_li3: 'Structural execution quality (entry conditions, exit logic)',
        fw_s07_li4: 'Behavioral discipline (absence of revenge trades, impulsive entries)',
        fw_s07_li5: 'Avoidance of overtrading',
        fw_s07_li6: 'Journaling consistency — every session must be documented',
        fw_s07_li7: 'Quality of self-review — periodic behavioral assessment is required',
        fw_s07_mandate: '<strong>Evaluation Standard:</strong> Financial performance is irrelevant if rules are violated. A participant who concludes the 2-month period with a 30% gain but documented rule violations has failed. A participant who concludes with a 10% loss and zero violations has passed.',
