        price_h2: 'Structure Your Participation',
        price_note: 'Access to Accessories is subscription-based and renews monthly. It is not included in any challenge product. Passing any ALTIVOR challenge unlocks the discounted rate of 59 &euro; / month for 12 months — applicable across all Accessories options. Subscribing directly at 79 &euro; / month requires no PREPARE qualification, no challenge participation, and no compliance rules — pure standalone access.',
